    {
      "text": "Join Mega Mega.EXE, his pal Lan and friends as they keep the net safe from cyber mayhem in the most expansive battle network adventure yet. Together with the White version, find all of Mega Man's battle style changes, \"Giga Class\" Chips, enemies and discover more surprises just for you!",
